  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cube Survivor is an engaging roguelite experience that challenges you to harness the power of your mouse and use a diverse array of unique abilities in your quest to protect your core from relentless enemy assaults.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Change forms</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664970/extras/311d4fbdabd12ef14cd319a0435a117a.poster.avif?t=1733511619\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664970/extras/311d4fbdabd12ef14cd319a0435a117a.webm?t=1733511619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664970/extras/311d4fbdabd12ef14cd319a0435a117a.mp4?t=1733511619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Alter your form and use it's ability to either stun, deal colossal damage, bolster your own defense or increase attack speed against your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock new abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664970/extras/e30a4f100f07cd89e784030ad1a85481.poster.avif?t=1733511619\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664970/extras/e30a4f100f07cd89e784030ad1a85481.webm?t=1733511619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664970/extras/e30a4f100f07cd89e784030ad1a85481.mp4?t=1733511619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Unlock and discover a diverse array of unique abilities to help you defend your core and defeat your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survive waves of enemies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664970/extras/12ceffcca5590fff4fe192f5bc2ebb5f.poster.avif?t=1733511619\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664970/extras/12ceffcca5590fff4fe192f5bc2ebb5f.webm?t=1733511619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664970/extras/12ceffcca5590fff4fe192f5bc2ebb5f.mp4?t=1733511619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Battle through waves of enemies with increasing difficulty and defend your core from an explosive death.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cube Survivor is an engaging roguelite experience that challenges you to harness the power of your mouse and use a diverse array of unique abilities in your quest to protect your core from relentless enemy assaults.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Change forms</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664970/extras/311d4fbdabd12ef14cd319a0435a117a.poster.avif?t=1733511619\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664970/extras/311d4fbdabd12ef14cd319a0435a117a.webm?t=1733511619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664970/extras/311d4fbdabd12ef14cd319a0435a117a.mp4?t=1733511619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Alter your form and use it's ability to either stun, deal colossal damage, bolster your own defense or increase attack speed against your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock new abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664970/extras/e30a4f100f07cd89e784030ad1a85481.poster.avif?t=1733511619\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664970/extras/e30a4f100f07cd89e784030ad1a85481.webm?t=1733511619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2664970/extras/e30a4f100f07cd89e784030ad1a85481.mp4?t=1733511619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Unlock and discover a diverse array of unique abilities to help you defend your core and defeat your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p